[Desktop Entry]
Name=Desktop Plus
Comment=GitHub Desktop fork with advanced functionality and improvements.
Comment[es]=Trabaja con GitHub desde tu escritorio.
Comment[eu]=GitHub-ekin lan egin zure ordenagailutik.
